{"tid":1026278,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果公司更新專利　未來iPhone或出摺機","createTime":"2019-02-18T03:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T18:11:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"daadfa9ec6e21d8c98deb8907374ac9ed22175fb","tid":1026278,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190218/s00010/f2b4de5ae277496da5ec32c8e2e34c29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190218%2Fs00010%2Ff2b4de5ae277496da5ec32c8e2e34c29.jpg&h=3313a7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果近年的手機創新程度被對手拉近，甚至有超越的情況，三星、華為等均有意趁下周舉行世界移動大會，發布其摺疊屏幕手機，而蘋果在這方面亦只聞樓梯響，今年秋季的新機似乎仍未見有摺機登場，最新亦只見其更新摺屏專利而已。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國專利及商標局資料，蘋果在14日時針對摺疊機相關專利進行更新，未來iPhone可望同時搭載內折和外折。今次有多個更新，包括顯示器向外和顯示器向內的兩種摺疊法；一種結合內折與外折的三塊摺疊面板；及手機螢幕變成可以摺疊的兩塊小螢幕。    <br />\n<br />\n據早前的市場傳聞，蘋果除了將技術用於iPhone上，MacBook和iPad亦有機會用上。"},{"pid":"d3796e2069ac881404cc47fc5a12e3be7275a36c","tid":1026278,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1550460980156&amp;issue=20190218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1550460980156%26issue%3D20190218&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgIbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=ea34616e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1550460980156%26issue%3D20190218&h=94c1f52a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1550460980156&amp;issue=20190218</a>"},{"pid":"03fbc9fec751c41bcc924134aa00753fc4508118","tid":1026278,"uid":27558,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbfe05639a0827ae503725b983a32e62dc68d43","tid":1026278,"uid":6211,"like":15,"dislike